26. How do you handle elements present inside frame?
        *   Locate the iframe
            frame1 = driver.find_element('loc_name', 'loc_value')
        *   Switch the driver to the frame
            driver.switch_to.frame(frame1)
        *   After switching, perform the operations inside the frame
        *   Once the operations are done, switch back to the parent_frame
            driver.switch_to.parent_frame()

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
