34. How to check if an element is visible on the web page?
        Solution1
        from selenium import webdriver
        from selenium.webdriver.support.ui import WebDriverWait
        from selenium.webdriver.support import expected_conditions

        driver = webdriver.Chrome()
        wait_ = WebDriverWait(driver, timeouttime)

        wait_.until(expected_conditions.visibility_of_element_located(('loc_name', 'loc_value'))

        Solution2
        element = driver.find_element("loc_name", "loc_value")
        element.is_displayed()

